These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, december, march, november
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in march##2
6. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | coffee     | hot-chocolate | mirinda |
| Birthday     | february     | march | november  | december      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, security-guard, engineer, photographer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, zombie, epic
1. the security-guard is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person watching epic movies is on the far left or far right##3
3. the photographer is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the engineer is on the far right##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Job   | dancer | security-guard    | photographer     | engineer  |
| Movie-Genre     | musical    | zombie | mystery | epic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, car, subway, skateboard
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, grey, yellow, azure
1. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
2. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
5. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Transport   | car   | subway   | motorbike  | skateboard |
| Color           | grey | azure | yellow | light-blue  |

