.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, kiwi, plum, banana
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, bus, tram, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person eating plum##1
2. the person eating banana is between the person eating pepper and the person driving the tram##2
3. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
4. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
5. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
6. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Food         | kiwi | pepper | banana | plum  |
| Transport   | bus  | ship   | scooter  | tram |

