.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, montecristo, dannemann, aristoff
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, february, december, july
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
4. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Cigar   | ritmeester    | montecristo   | dannemann | aristoff    |
| Birthday      | february | january | december       | july |

