.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, writer, manager, chef
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, thriller, family, zombie
1. the chef is on the right of the manager##1
2. the person watching family movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the manager##2
3. the person watching western movies is between the person watching family movies and the journalist##2
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
5. the writer is on the left or right of the chef##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Job    | journalist | manager | chef | writer |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | western  | family    | zombie  |

