.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, tea, cola, 7up
4 different pets are kept: goat, lizard, horse, frog
1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking 7up##2
5. the owner of the lizard is the owner of the lizard##1
6. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the horse and the person drinking 7up##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | 7up | cola | tea     |
| Pet     | goat | frog  | lizard   | horse |

