.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, bellflower, iris, rose
4 different pets are kept: goat, bird, chinchilla, ferret
1. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
2. the person who growsrose is the owner of the bird##1
3. the person who growsrose is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
5. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Flower         | rose | iris | zinnia | bellflower   |
| Pet   | bird | chinchilla | goat      | ferret |

