2. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the airplane is the fan of country##1
4. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of pop##1
5. the fan of techno is on the far left or far right##3
6. the fan of pop is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the roller##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre     | techno | pop   | folk      | country      |
| Transport   | scooter     | helicopter | roller | airplane |

