3. the person who growsamaryllis is the person who likes turquise##1
4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
5. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
