.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, domino, snooker, go
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, water, fanta, cola
1. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person playing domino is the person drinking cola##1
4. the person drinking water is the person playing snooker##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
6. the person drinking fanta is the person playing monopoly##1
7. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Game         | domino | go | snooker | monopoly |
| Beverage   | cola     | sprite       | water   | fanta      |

