.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-17::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, handball, tennis, badminton
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, japanese, indonesian, turkish
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the turkish is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the japanese##3
4. the japanese is on the right of the russian##1
5. the indonesian is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Sport      | lacrosse | handball    | badminton  | tennis |
| Nationality   | russian       | japanese | indonesian | turkish  |

