4. the person playing bridge is on the left of the american##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Nationality   | spanish        | dutch       | american   | german |
| Game    | canasta | bridge | domino | chess  |

