.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, baccarat, game, bluemaster
4 different pets are kept: lizard, dog, snake, fish
1. the owner of the snake is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the fish is the owner of the fish##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
4. the owner of the lizard is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
6. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
7. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Cigar   | baccarat     | vegafina     | game          | bluemaster |
| Pet      | lizard | dog | fish | snake  |

 